instructions: On your phone, open the Settings app . Under "Personal," tap Location . Turn on location.

On your phone, touch & hold the Home button or say "Ok Google." Say, for example: "I parked here" "Remember where I parked" "I parked my car on level two" "I parked in the south lot" "My parking spot is F34" To type instead, tap Type .
On your phone, touch & hold the Home button or say "Ok Google." Ask, for example: "Where s my car?" "Where did I park?" "Do you remember where I parked?" To type instead, tap Type .
